05:12.478 --> 05:15.732
I promised Sage I'd help him look
for a new location for his kingdom.

05:15.815 --> 05:17.442
Since Koto burned his down.

05:17.525 --> 05:21.321
So, uh, you two are
house hunting together?

05:21.404 --> 05:24.115
Yeah. No! I mean... It's, ooh, it's ju...

05:24.198 --> 05:27.660
Oh. Clover's got a boy--

05:28.494 --> 05:33.207
No. Sage and I are colleagues.
Uh, nothing else. But for the record.

05:33.583 --> 05:37.128
The people are idiots, Your Majesty.
Incapable of governing themselves.

05:37.211 --> 05:39.005
This will end in disaster.

05:39.088 --> 05:41.549
So you think my idea is genius?

05:42.967 --> 05:44.093
See you in a week.

05:44.594 --> 05:45.970
I'm okay.

05:51.601 --> 05:53.436
Hello, Mort!

05:53.519 --> 05:58.107
Zora, please, I'm working.
King Julien is desperate

05:58.191 --> 06:00.735
