But I... Where did you fi... uh...

08:02.398 --> 08:07.570
Hello, Miss Clover. Hope you, uh,
don't mind me lending lendin' a hand?

08:07.653 --> 08:10.823
Captain

08:10.907 --> 08:15.119
Just got my certification.
Figured I've plundered enough kingdoms

08:15.203 --> 08:16.287
