08:16.370 --> 08:20.166
He says with all the recent carnage
and destruction, it's a buyers' market.

08:20.917 --> 08:22.168
Right.

08:22.251 --> 08:25.505
So are, uh, you two looking
for something together,

08:25.588 --> 08:28.174
