Doctor S, but I just ate.

10:50.232 --> 10:53.903
No problem.
We're gonna be here for a while.

10:53.986 --> 10:56.906
Nurse Phantom, start the saw!

11:01.869 --> 11:06.624
Ah! Smell that, Maurice?
No conflict even makes the air better.

11:06.707 --> 11:09.877
Actually, I think it's the new
toilet cakes in the outhouses.

11:09.960 --> 11:11.754
What was that?

11:11.837 --> 11:13.255
Take that back!

11:13.339 --> 11:18.135
