They will pay! Pay!

11:19.220 --> 11:21.430
Pancho What's going on?

11:21.514 --> 11:22.348
Ask Horst.

11:22.431 --> 11:27.061
Yeah, he wanted a sip from
my beverage and I said no.

11:27.144 --> 11:29.605
