12:24.118 --> 12:26.704
Cantaloupe

12:26.787 --> 12:28.664
Hector had a bad experience.

12:29.206 --> 12:34.003
Why are you here?
What do you want from me?

12:34.545 --> 12:36.797
King Julien,
I'm all for a conflict-free kingdom,

12:36.881 --> 12:40.134
but how are we supposed to monitor
people from saying all these words?

12:40.217 --> 12:45.681
Lemurs of Madagascar,
concern over certain hurtful words

12:45.764 --> 12:47.600
has come to my attention.

12:47.683 --> 12:51.145
But never fear, your sensitive
and understanding King

12:51.228 --> 12:56.108
has found a solution.
I give to you, the victim horn!

12:56.192 --> 12:58.402
What are we gonna do with that?

12:58.486 --> 13:02.448
I need a volunteer to read
from a prepared script.

13:02.531 --> 13:07.745
Me! Me! Oh, please let it be me!
You don't know how much I need this!

13:07.828 --> 13:11.040
Oh. Not much of a part.
How long do I have to prepare?

13:11.123 --> 13:12.458
Just read the script, Ted!

13:14.043 --> 13:19.715
"Hey, Maurice, did you swallow a melon
or is your tummy really that--"

13:19.798 --> 13:21.008
-Ow!

13:21.091 --> 13:22.051
Hoo-hoo!

13:22.218 --> 13:26.514
Did you see that?
Whenever someone utters a hurtful word...

13:27.598 --> 13:31.519
you just blast the word away
with your victim horn and sha-booya!

13:31.602 --> 13:36.023
The word never existed.
Who wants to do some horning?

13:41.654 --> 13:45.866
A kingdom full of horn-blasting lemurs.
Oh, yeah, this isn't gonna be a disaster.

13:49.119 --> 13:53.290
I hope the water is warmer than yesterday.
I nearly froze my

