13:59.672 --> 14:02.341
You mean you weren't going to say--

14:02.424 --> 14:05.261
No, you moron, I was gonna say--

14:09.223 --> 14:10.432
Good night, Dorothy.

14:10.516 --> 14:13.394
Good night, Ted. I love--

14:13.477 --> 14:16.981
So I said to Becca, "You know what that's
called a tossed salad."

14:17.064 --> 14:18.649
Which meant I had to get the dressing.

14:18.732 --> 14:20.276
And that's when I realized...

14:20.359 --> 14:22.653
I didn't have any dressing.

14:22.736 --> 14:25.656
But that didn't make sense. Crazy, huh?

14:25.865 --> 14:27.032
Uh-huh.

14:27.116 --> 14:32.538
And that's why we now have proof
that life began because of a big--

14:33.831 --> 14:36.000
I'm sorry, did I say a hurt word?

14:37.167 --> 14:38.294
Because I'm pretty sure--

14:38.377 --> 14:40.421
We weren't questioning your words.

14:40.504 --> 14:42.840
We were questioning your syntax.

14:43.340 --> 14:46.719
Your word sentences
is causing us distress!

14:46.802 --> 14:50.139
Yeah!
Stop treading on us with your knowledge!

14:51.974 --> 14:54.602
Do you hear that, Maurice?

14:54.685 --> 14:57.605
That's the sound
of no conflict right there.

14:57.688 --> 14:58.647
That's what that is.

14:58.731 --> 15:02.568
If you think that's the sound
of no conflict, you crazy!

15:05.863 --> 15:09.533
Now this first kingdom
is a bit of a fixer-upper.

15:09.617 --> 15:12.995
What are you talking about?
This is perfect!

15:14.330 --> 15:15.956
It's a lifeless desert, Sage.

15:16.040 --> 15:19.543
I know. We should move on this
before someone else makes a bid.

15:21.921 --> 15:23.047
What else you got?

15:25.174 --> 15:28.177
Whoa! A tree fort. Cool.

15:29.094 --> 15:30.804
Hello, neighbors.

15:34.308 --> 15:35.142
Next!

15:35.976 --> 15:40.230
This one just came on the market.
It's a subterranean lair, air cooled

15:40.314 --> 15:44.818
